==German==
===Verb===
'''strecken'''

# to [[straighten]], [[stretch]]
#:''Sie streckte ihre m&uuml;den Glieder.'' - She stretched her tired limbs.
# to [[elongate]], [[lengthen]]
# to [[dilute]]
#:''Er streckte den Wein mit Wasser.'' - He diluted the wine with water.

